<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2 style="font-size: 24px">Hi <%= @user.first_name %></h2>
    <p>
        We’re thrilled to have you as a new user. You’re one step closer to meeting cool people who love the same awesome things as you. After you’ve clicked the confirmation link, you're all set!
    </p>
    <p>
      <b><%= link_to 'Click here to activate your account.', ('www.cliqwith.me' + activate_path(id: @user.id, code: @user.activation)) %></b><br> 
    </p>
    <p>
      This is an automatically generated email, so please don’t reply to it! If you are having trouble activating your account, write to us at support@cliqwith.me and we'll help you out.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining and have fun!</p>

    <p>-Cliq</p>
  </body>
</html>